  "text": "Previous research on the price characteristic relationship includes research on cow-calf pairs [CITATION_1] , purebred bulls [CITATION_2] , and feeder calves [CITATION_3] . This research follows prior research by [CITATION_4] that examined characteristics (heifer characteristics, calf and carcass expected characteristics, and market factors) that impact heifer/cow price variation.",
